parameters.query:
SELECT t.*, pm.* FROM trades t
JOIN position_monitoring pm ON t.id = pm.trade_id
WHERE t.status = 'FILLED' 
AND pm.monitoring_active = true
AND DATE(t.timestamp) = CURRENT_DATE

SELECT COUNT(*) as alert_count 
FROM position_alerts 
WHERE trade_id = {{ $json.trade_id }}
AND alert_type = '{{ $json.alert_type }}'
AND timestamp > NOW() - INTERVAL '30 minutes'
